OL,3,CSub-postmaster suffered racist abuse
OL,4,Cafter wrongful conviction
OL,6,FA wrongly convicted postmaster told
OL,7,FITV News that the mistrust and
OL,8,Fsuspicion piled upon him saw his once
OL,9,Fpeaceful village life blighted by
OL,10,Fabuse and harrasment, as Nick Wallis
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThirteen years ago, Vipin Patel was
OL,14,Fsuicidal. He'd been convicted of
OL,15,Fstealing #34,000 from the branch he
OL,16,Fran in Horspath, Oxfordshire.
OL,18,FThe Patels were the only Asian family
OL,19,Fin the village. Shortly after Vipin's
OL,20,Fconviction, a sign was placed on the
OL,21,FPatels' shop door.
