OL,6,FIt read: "Wanted: Dead or Alive. Post
OL,7,FOffice Robber. If you know where this
OL,8,Fperson could be found, you could get a
OL,9,Freward of a #10,000 Giro! Be Warned,
OL,10,Fhe can be Dangerous."
OL,12,FVipin describes it as a stressful
OL,13,Ftime. "Every morning you wake up, you
OL,14,Fhad this feeling like stomach-churning
OL,15,Fand body not wanting to get up because
OL,16,Fyou didn't know how to face the day."
