OL,6,FJayshree, Vipin's wife, believes there
OL,7,Fwas malign intent behind the poster.
OL,8,F"Someone in the village... a very
OL,9,Fnasty person... they wanted Vipin (to)
OL,10,Fdie."
OL,12,FAround this time Jayshree says she was
OL,13,Fracially abused by a customer as she
OL,14,Fworked behind the counter in the shop.
OL,16,FMany Horspath residents saw their
OL,17,Fvillage Post Office as an important
OL,18,Fresource and didn't want to lose it.
