OL,6,FThe Patels came under pressure to let
OL,7,Fa different sub-postmaster run the
OL,8,Fbranch from within their shop. Vipin
OL,9,Frefused. It didn't make financial
OL,10,Fsense.
OL,12,FAn email exchange between two
OL,13,Fvillagers, seen by ITV News, disagreed
OL,14,Fwith Vipin's assessment. "Your reading
OL,15,Fof economics is actually spot on,"
OL,16,Fwrote one correspondent "but you have
OL,17,Foverlooked one thing... east is east
OL,18,Fand west is west!"
