OL,6,FThe same email also (mystifyingly)
OL,7,Fnotes that Vipin and Jayshree's
OL,8,Fchildren "are now earning money in the
OL,9,Fbig wide world, and we all understand
OL,10,Fthe culture."
OL,12,FAnother email sent to Horspath Parish
OL,13,FCouncil suggests the Patels'
OL,14,Fpermission to use village-owned land
OL,15,Ffor customer parking and access to
OL,16,Ftheir private driveway should be
OL,17,Frevoked. "I am sorry" writes the
OL,18,Femail's author, "but there has to be a
OL,19,Frealistic stick."
