OL,6,FOnce it became apparent the Patels
OL,7,Fwere not going to allow a Post Office
OL,8,Fto be run from their premises, some
OL,9,Fvillagers wanted them to sell up and
OL,10,Fleave. An estate agent's "for sale"
OL,11,Fsign was hammered into the ground
OL,12,Foutside their shop.
OL,14,F"The idea was to drive us out." says
OL,15,FVipin, "Frightening us to any extent
OL,16,F(to) get results."
