OL,6,FThe Patels refused to countenance
OL,7,Freturning to London where they had
OL,8,Flived and worked before buying
OL,9,FHorspath Village Stores. But it was
OL,10,Ftough.
OL,12,FIn 2016, five years after Vipin's
OL,13,Fconviction, a memorial cross was
OL,14,Fcemented into a section of land
OL,15,Fdirectly outside Horspath Village
OL,16,FStores. On the cross was written "RIP
OL,17,FVIPIN."
