OL,6,FVipin described his alarm on seeing
OL,7,Fthe cross for the first time: "I was
OL,8,Fstill being treated for depression and
OL,9,Fsuicidal counselling... this was
OL,10,Fanother big blow"
OL,12,FKeith Woods is a Horspath resident and
OL,13,Ffriend of Vipin's. He has no doubt
OL,14,Fracism played a part in the treatment
OL,15,Fof the Patels. "Definitely," Keith
OL,16,Ftold me, "because he's a foreigner...
OL,17,For Asian. If he'd have been an
OL,18,FEnglishman or white man they'd
OL,19,Fprobably look at it a little bit
OL,20,Fdifferently."
