OL,6,FIn the months after Vipin's
OL,7,Fconviction, whilst he was battling his
OL,8,Fmental health, Jayshree kept the show
OL,9,Fon the road, working long hours in the
OL,10,Fshop.
OL,12,FShe would find herself checking on
OL,13,FVipin every half hour, worried he
OL,14,Fmight harm himself if he was left
OL,15,Falone for too long.
OL,17,FJayshree told me that sometimes she
OL,18,Fwould install Vipin behind the counter
OL,19,Fin the shop so she could go upstairs
OL,20,Fto cry.
