OL,6,FThe couple's son, Varchas, was 23 at
OL,7,Fthe time of Vipin's conviction and
OL,8,Fliving in London. He said his parents
OL,9,Ftried to shield him from what they
OL,10,Fwere going through, particularly
OL,11,FJayshree. "She didn't need to do
OL,12,Fthat," he told me "She could have come
OL,13,Fto me for help."
OL,15,FOf those in the village who made Vipin
OL,16,Fand Jayshree feel unwelcome, Varchas
OL,17,Fsays "they all should be ashamed of
OL,18,Fthemselves."
