OL,6,FThe Patels are keen to stress that the
OL,7,Fmajority of the people in Horspath
OL,8,Fhave not caused them any problems and
OL,9,Fthey have been able to build a
OL,10,Fsuccessful business, despite Vipin's
OL,11,Fconviction and the closure of his Post
OL,12,FOffice branch.
OL,14,FIn 2020, I travelled to Horspath on
OL,15,Fthe day Vipin's conviction was quashed
OL,16,Fand witnessed a celebration as a
OL,17,Fstream of villagers came to the shop
OL,18,Fto shake Vipin's hand and take
OL,19,Fphotographs of the Patels, who were
OL,20,Fbeaming with delight.
