OL,6,FThe Patels say everything has changed
OL,7,Fagain since the ITV drama, Mr Bates vs
OL,8,FThe Post Office, with people sending
OL,9,Fletters of support and former
OL,10,Fvillagers going out of their way to
OL,11,Fdrop by their shop to wish them well.
OL,13,FWhen we contacted the Post Office for
OL,14,Fcomment, it said "we are deeply sorry
OL,15,Ffor the pain which has been suffered
OL,16,Fby so many people, their families and
OL,17,Ffriends throughout the Horizon IT
OL,18,FScandal."
