OL,6,FThe Post Office also told us that
OL,7,Fsince being appointed, its chief
OL,8,Fexecutive has met a number of former
OL,9,FSubpostmasters as he believes its
OL,10,F"important to understand the trauma
OL,11,Fthat people have gone through".
OL,13,FWhen I asked the Patels if they
OL,14,Fthought the Post Office had any idea
OL,15,Fwhat it had done by pursuing hundreds
OL,16,Fof innocent people through the
OL,17,Fcriminal courts, Vipin said: "No. They
OL,18,Fhaven't got a clue, because they work
OL,19,Fin ivory towers and we are small
OL,20,Fpeople.
